{"tid":2479150,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"記者協會譴責故意干擾CCTVB 新聞直播","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T15:27:29.000Z","uid":184261,"like":18,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f384f476f98c41bcd4b91becfc9285d0acdc8234","tid":2479150,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"聲明:記協譴責故意干擾新聞直播的行為<br />\n<br />\n無綫新聞記者今晚(4月7 日) 在屯門友愛邨進行新聞直播期間，有市民高聲呼喊及跑到鏡頭前高舉不雅手勢，干擾新聞直播進行，最終無綫新聞需要中斷現場直播。<br />\n<br />\n本會譴責此等阻礙新聞工作者履行職務的行為，要求各方立即停止任何針對新聞工作者的阻礙或干擾，讓前綫新聞工作者均能有效地履行其第四權天職。<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會<br />\n2021年4月7日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/242729300308/posts/10159023051625309/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F242729300308%2Fposts%2F10159023051625309%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYYVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=f71f8891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/242729300308/posts/10159023051625309/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d403dbe0016aa04ecead313d24821f204494aea3","tid":2479150,"uid":59976,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:11:38.000Z","msg":"記協好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61a19035578999bca40ee02eb1af0ab98edffd8","tid":2479150,"uid":207846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:11:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c2ae1633276cf5a2f6535e40d728deee4768c3","tid":2479150,"uid":181581,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"手足勿分化🙏🏻"},{"pid":"4ff9c4703fdd49b8d15e